<p>The <code>@even</code> property returns TRUE if the current occurrence number is even.</p>

<h2>Zebra Striping</h2>
<pre>{open}users{close}
  &lt;tr class="{open}@even ? even : odd{close}"&gt;
    &lt;td&gt;{open}$name{close}&lt;/td&gt;
  &lt;/tr&gt;
{open}/users{close}</pre>

<p>Result:</p>
<style>.even { background: #e0e0e0; } .odd { background: #ffffff; }</style>
<table border="1">
  <tr><th>Name</th></tr>
{users}
  <tr class="{@even ? even : odd}">
    <td>{$name}</td>
  </tr>
{/users}
</table>

<h2>Even Items Only</h2>
<pre>{open}colors{close}
  {open}@even{close}
    &lt;li&gt;{open}@current{close}. {open}$colors{close}&lt;/li&gt;
  {open}/@even{close}
{open}/colors{close}</pre>

<p>Result (only even positions):</p>
<ul>
{colors}
  {@even}
    <li>{@current}. {$colors}</li>
  {/@even}
{/colors}
</ul>
